00:24:30.770 --> 00:24:31.740
By the way,

00:24:31.740 --> 00:24:37.400
have you two heard the rumor about humans coming to our island to hunt merfolk?

00:24:40.260 --> 00:24:43.036
Den, where did you hear that?

00:24:43.036 --> 00:24:46.080
The last time I went to shed my toxins,

00:24:46.080 --> 00:24:51.686
I overheard some of the others saying that
