00:31:57.740 --> 00:32:00.180
He's a pretty big deal around here.

00:32:00.890 --> 00:32:05.341
He's nice, good-looking, and rich.

00:32:05.341 --> 00:32:07.370
Plus, he and Phana have been close
since they were kids.

00:32:07.370 --> 00:32:10.930
But then again, Koh Khen is a small island.

00:32:11.510 --> 00:32:13.510
So he's friends with Nava?

00:32:14.310 --> 00:32:19.476
To Nava, Phraphai is like another older brother.

00:32:19.476 --> 00:32:22.520
- An older brother?
- Yeah.

00:32:22.520 --> 00:32:24.680
But it's not the same
as his relationship with Phana.

00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:26.780
How should I put it...

00:32:27.500 --> 00:32:29.500
Well, to be honest,

00:32:29.500 --> 00:32:31.920
