Let me ask you something directly.

00:34:21.820 --> 00:34:25.640
Everything you're doing...
Are you hitting on me?

00:34:28.970 --> 00:34:30.727
Yes.

00:34:30.727 --> 00:34:33.080
I'm hitting on you.

00:34:36.200 --> 00:34:38.460
I think he is.

00:34:38.460 --> 00:34:41.490
At first, I thought he was just messing around,

00:34:41.490 --> 00:34:45.020
but when I asked him about it,
he said he was serious.

00:34:45.020 --> 00:34:46.660
And...

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:51.400
